{"tid":2390944,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[AAPL]實測 iOS 14.5 戴口罩用 Apple Watch 助 iPhone 解鎖功能","createTime":"2021-02-02T01:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T02:00:42.000Z","uid":2638,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"63a5d6f6a77f6f15c334512ab5faded686b359b8","tid":2390944,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:41:16.000Z","msg":"實測 iOS 14.5 戴口罩用 Apple Watch 助 iPhone 解鎖功能<br />\n自從疫情開始，戴口罩已成為人們生活的一部份。不過對於 Face ID 用戶來說，戴口罩後解鎖成為最煩惱的事情。因為 Face ID 沒有因為疫情而降低安全度，往往需要用戶手動輸入密碼解鎖。<br />\n<br />\n今天，iOS 14.5 引進了新功能，如果 Apple Watch （watchOS 7.4) 用戶戴口罩時用解鎖 iPhone，可直接透過 Apple Watch 解鎖，那就是只要戴上 Apple Watch，你就可以免輸入密碼為 iPhone 解鎖了！<br />\n<br />\n實測感受：超方便的體驗<br />\n筆者戴上口罩時而同時戴上 Apple Watch，只要如常拿起 iPhone 向上撥，Face ID 會立即通過。這種久違的方便感受終於回來了！<br />\n<br />\n仍需 Face ID Apple Watch 只作輔助<br />\n不少人好奇，其實戴上口罩後，iPhone 是否變相透過 Apple Watch 解鎖？就好像 Mac 一般？其實並非如此， Face ID 仍需要偵測你的外觀，Apple Watch 只是作「部份」的補完。假設你將 iPhone 拿給別人，由於 Face ID 覺得這用戶跟「主人」完全不同，不會因為你戴上 Apple Watch 而讓你解鎖。"},{"pid":"d840a1957b561f86c4065e774918b1a28b2ee403","tid":2390944,"uid":146267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:48:27.000Z","msg":"聽講可以雙卡5G了？唔知幾時有得up🤔"},{"pid":"1628c9266e87022cdfc8c5a4338cad091ac15e9d","tid":2390944,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d840a1957b561f86c4065e774918b1a28b2ee403","tid":2390944,"uid":146267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:48:27.000Z","msg":"聽講可以雙卡5G了？唔知幾時有得up🤔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:49:58.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"f4fd63a6c6ff1158f0f2bf7b27ad8fa40678d166","tid":2390944,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:59:19.000Z","msg":"想買iwatch🤤"},{"pid":"63282679da201d94a95344adc39cf0f0bc97db44","tid":2390944,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4fd63a6c6ff1158f0f2bf7b27ad8fa40678d166","tid":2390944,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T01:59:19.000Z","msg":"想買iwatch🤤"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T02:00:42.000Z","msg":"profit <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}